Definition: without care or thought for others
Example: the thoughtless saying of a great princess on being informed that the people had no bread; `Let them eat cake'
Synonyms: noun, attribute, thoughtlessness, uncaring, unthinking, without, care, or, thought, for, others, the, saying, of, a, great, princess, on, being, informed, that, people, had, no, bread, Let, them, eat, cake
Category: adj.all
